### Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "testuser",
    "password": "testuser"
}

### Set auth token from login response
@auth_token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Register
POST http://localhost:8000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "johndoe",
    "password": "your_password",
    "email": "john@example.com"
}

### Get All Posts
GET http://localhost:8000/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Get My Posts
GET http://localhost:8000/me/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### Create Post
POST http://localhost:8000/posts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
    "title": "My First Post",
    "content": "This is the content of my post",
    "tags": ["technology", "programming"]
}

### Edit Post
PUT http://localhost:8000/posts/123
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
    "title": "Updated Post Title",
    "content": "Updated content of my post",
    "tags": ["technology", "programming", "golang"]
}

### Delete Post
DELETE http://localhost:8000/posts/123
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}